#. Tag: title
#: introduction.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:3
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&partman; is a utility program to help you manage the <glossterm linkend="
"\"glossary-device\">disk devices</glossterm>, <glossterm linkend=\"glossary-"
"partition\">partitions</glossterm> and <glossterm linkend=\"glossary-"
"filesystem\">file systems</glossterm> on your computer."
msgstr ""
"&partman; je pomožni program, ki vam pomaga upravljati <glossterm linkend="
"\"glossary-device\">diskovne naprave</glossterm>, <glossterm linkend="
"\"glossary-partition\">particije</glossterm> in <glossterm linkend="
"\"glossary-filesystem\">datotečne sisteme</glossterm> v vašem računalniku."

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:6
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It allows you to easily <link linkend=\"howto-installos\">create new "
"partitions</link>, create file systems on new or existing partitions, <link "
"linkend=\"howto-copypartition\">copy</link>, move or delete partitions and "
"also to <link linkend=\"howto-resizepartition\">modify a partition's size</"
"link> without losing the data on it."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča enostavno <link linkend=\"howto-installos\">ustvarjanje novih "
"particij</link>, ustvarjanje datotečnih sistemov na novih ali obstoječih "
"particijah, <link linkend=\"howto-copypartition\">kopiranje</link>, "
"premikanje ali brisanje particij in tudi za <link linkend=\"howto-"
"resizepartition\">spreminjanje velikosti particije</link>, ne da bi pri tem "
"izgubili podatke na njej."

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To get its job done efficiently &partman; makes use of external tools to "
"support a long list of file systems. You will probably have the required "
"tools for the file systems on your computer installed already."
msgstr ""
"Za učinkovito opravljanje svojega dela &partman; uporablja zunanja orodja za "
"podporo dolgemu seznamu datotečnih sistemov. Verjetno boste že imeli "
"nameščena potrebna orodja za datotečne sisteme v vašem računalniku."

#. Tag: title
#: introduction.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid "Always back up your data!"
msgstr "Vedno varnostno kopirajte svoje podatke!"

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&partman; has been designed and written with high diligence and an emphasis "
"on data integrity. There is however always some danger involved when "
"modifying a device's partition table or its partitions: There might still be "
"a bug in &partman;, an unexpected power failure or a problem with the "
"computer's hardware."
msgstr ""
"&partman; je bil zasnovan in napisan z veliko skrbnostjo in poudarkom na "
"celovitosti podatkov. Pri spreminjanju tabele particij naprave ali njenih "
"particij pa vedno obstaja nekaj nevarnosti: morda je še vedno napaka v "
"&partman;u, nepričakovan izpad električne energije ali težava s strojno "
"opremo računalnika."

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For those reasons you should <emphasis>always have a back up of your "
"important data</emphasis> before making any modifications with a tool like "
"&partman;."
msgstr ""
"Zaradi teh razlogov morate <emphasis>vedno imeti varnostno kopijo vaših "
"pomembnih podatkov</emphasis>, preden naredite kakršne koli spremembe z "
"orodjem, kot je &partman;."

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The program's authors take no responsibility whatsoever if you lose any data "
"while using &partman;."
msgstr ""
"Avtorji programa ne prevzemajo nobene odgovornosti, če med uporabo &partman; "
"izgubite podatke."

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&partman; uses <glossterm linkend=\"glossary-operation\">operations</"
"glossterm>, <glossterm linkend=\"glossary-job\">jobs</glossterm> and "
"<glossterm linkend=\"glossary-command\">commands</glossterm> to logically "
"divide up the work it does. See the <link linkend=\"glossary\">glossary</"
"link> for details on this."
msgstr ""
"&partman; uporablja <glossterm linkend=\"glossary-operation\">operacije</"
"glossterm>, <glossterm linkend=\"glossary-job\">opravila</glossterm> in "
"<glossterm linkend=\"glossary-command\">ukaze</glossterm> da logično razdeli "
"delo, ki ga opravlja. Za podrobnosti o tem glejte <link linkend=\"glossary"
"\">glosar</link>."
